intent_context: Received a letter about the new Vacatia Clubhouse and is having trouble with the ID and registration process
steps: Identify intent to register for Clubhouse
Verify customer identity via name, phone, and state
Clarify difference between RCI ID and Vacatia ID
Confirm email address for sending link

clarifications.note: Agent re-verified spelling of last name
Confirmed if customer wanted registration link

corrections.note: Customer corrected spelling of last name

summary: Customer called frustrated because they couldn't register for the new Clubhouse portal using their RCI ID. The agent verified the account, explained the ID difference, and was in the process of sending a registration link when the call ended.
verbatim: I type in the code that I got from the code, and it says it's not no good... It's ridiculous.

actions.detail: Confirmed email but call ended before confirmation
